Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Avant--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去刷牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒忘拿什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,忘拿月票了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
