Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,480)\fad(500,0)\blur2\fsp10}再見了 吹奏樂大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晴香 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,穿這個還真是熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,已經在吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這就開始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 也太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.45,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fsp40\frz31.5\pos(586,540)}樂譜封套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 這個要放進哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,得問一下名來前輩才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,跟木槌放一起可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,話說名來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大概還沒來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,來太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,各分部組長 請確認自己的組員是否已到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打擊樂小組沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,長笛小組全體到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,單簧管小組到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,低音管和雙簧管小組都在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,長號小組到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,圓號小組到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,低音小組都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…薩克斯小組也到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…七點後會有卡車過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在車到達前十分鐘開始準備搬運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家聽從樂器搬運負責人的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,迅速把樂器裝上車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,樂譜負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始發樂譜封套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,請各分部組長上前領取
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,領到之後注意不要弄丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,負責搬運樂器的同學請到這邊集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,給 黃前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這是樂譜封套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我把這個搬走沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先裝打擊樂器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要是在氣勢上就輸了我可饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全員到齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這兩位的反差還是一如既往地大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他穿了晚禮服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚禮服啊 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 我能說幾句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,森田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,中川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…我們替補成員組成的「森中小隊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為大家做了護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在就發給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家收下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上面標了大家的姓名首字母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,給 廣江學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字縮寫不是「L.O.」是「R.O.」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是平文式拼法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,紗奈學姐 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺只有我的這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這是愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,名為「惡作劇」的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,高阪同學 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,還有高阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆的是異色的一對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下還有小綠和塚本同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都拿到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 我想她們每天練習到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還為所有人準備了這些真的很不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們 鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我們差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小笠原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,作為部長給大家說幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 等好久了 部長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,少揶揄我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就讓你替我講了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,咳咳 那麼就講講悠風號的歷史…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,別說那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 在準備今天的正式比賽的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而今天 今天我們能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是把迄今為止的努力 信念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,全部灌注到演奏中去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大家一起把口號喊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,北宇治Fight——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們的新月即將在會場中起舞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太吵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？我有藥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子 你在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了 是因為在想「不能失敗」才會緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要想著「見識一下我的演奏技巧吧」就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小綠真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 綠十分期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好想趕快開始演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\c&H282323&\bord0\fsp20\pos(994,378)}禁止演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好 各分部組長再次確認成員是否到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,清點結束後再確認一下樂器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是立華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,果然好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這裡集合 別站散了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,樂器齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,負責搬運樂器的同學們 我們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我紮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,紮緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,黃前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,中川學姐真是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,該過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 等這扇門關上後 就可以奏出聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,音沒調準…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來來 再聽一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好像稍微有些高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其實 雖然我想了很久要在這裡說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是沒有太多要講的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這個春天 你們決定要以全國大賽為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱著上進心努力至今
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,演奏出了美妙音樂的 是在場的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,請為自己而驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是北宇治高級中學吹奏樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就快到正式演出了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好讓觀眾大吃一驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,又倒退回最初的狀態去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我在問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好讓觀眾大吃一驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼各位 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,向著全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正式演出 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 會很順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,像平時一樣演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺如何？沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不像沒問題的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都練習得那麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,北宇治的各位 請
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Part B--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得有些寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如此快樂的時光就要結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這個夏天能永遠持續下去該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可不是最後一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是要參加全國大賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 那才是我們的目標啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第五支隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,北宇治高級中學吹奏樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在四號規定曲目後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,將演奏由堀川奈美惠作曲的「新月之舞」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,指揮是瀧升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能進入全國大賽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,從初中開始我就這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:20.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1800,0)\fn@Hiragino Sans GB W6\fsp20\frz256\fs30\c&H4A5A63&\3c&H83C5E1&\move(312,430,382,430)}悠風號教程
